Metallgesellschaft AG &lt;METG.F> saidit is founding a company to work in commodities futures andoptions trading and financial services linked to these.    The new company, to be called &lt;MG Commodity Corp>, will bebased in Zug, Switzerland, and operate from a branch inHamburg.    Metallgesellschaft will hold 80 pct of the company, and theother 20 pct will be held by Dieter Worms. REUTER&#3;